      "content": "but what if my presence is what's hurting them? i look at them and i just see how much better they'd be if i wasn't constantly dragging them down with my mess. it's like i'm just a weight around their necks. sometimes i honestly think the only way i could actually help them is to just... stop being a part of their lives. to stop being the problem.",
